<p data-start="33" data-end="58"><strong data-start="33" data-end="58">Smart AI Food Advisor</strong></p>
<p data-start="60" data-end="145">It <strong data-start="63" data-end="144">analyzes the food a user eats and evaluates nutrition based on the user's BMI</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="147" data-end="210">Let me help you phrase it <strong data-start="173" data-end="209">clearly for your website and PPT</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="212" data-end="215">
<h1 data-start="217" data-end="255">📌 Simple Explanation of Your System</h1>
<p data-start="257" data-end="286">Your website works like this:</p>
<p data-start="288" data-end="576">1️⃣ User logs in<br data-start="304" data-end="307">
2️⃣ User enters <strong data-start="323" data-end="363">health details (height, weight, age)</strong><br data-start="363" data-end="366">
3️⃣ System calculates <strong data-start="388" data-end="413">BMI (Body Mass Index)</strong><br data-start="413" data-end="416">
4️⃣ User uploads <strong data-start="433" data-end="447">food image</strong><br data-start="447" data-end="450">
5️⃣ AI detects the <strong data-start="469" data-end="482">food item</strong><br data-start="482" data-end="485">
6️⃣ System calculates <strong data-start="507" data-end="529">nutritional values</strong><br data-start="529" data-end="532">
7️⃣ Based on BMI, it shows <strong data-start="559" data-end="576">health advice</strong></p>
<hr data-start="578" data-end="581">
<h1 data-start="583" data-end="618">🍎 What Your System Actually Does</h1>
<p data-start="620" data-end="653">Your system answers the question:</p>
<p data-start="655" data-end="696"><strong data-start="655" data-end="696">"Is this food healthy for this user?"</strong></p>
<p data-start="698" data-end="749">Because nutrition needs depend on <strong data-start="732" data-end="748">BMI category</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="751" data-end="754">
