<p data-start="3350" data-end="3415">The <strong data-start="3354" data-end="3395">iPhone image will display your app UI</strong> like the reference.</p>
<hr data-start="3417" data-end="3420">
<h1 data-start="3422" data-end="3432">⭐ Result</h1>
<p data-start="3434" data-end="3471">Your landing page will now look like:</p>
