Your <strong data-start="69" data-end="97">CSS is not being applied</strong>, so the page is showing <strong data-start="122" data-end="145">default HTML styles</strong> (blue links, stacked layout, no flex layout).</p>
<p data-start="193" data-end="257">That means the browser is <strong data-start="219" data-end="256">not loading <code data-start="233" data-end="244">style.css</code> correctly</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="259" data-end="272">Let’s fix it.</p>
<hr data-start="274" data-end="277">
<h1 data-start="279" data-end="315">1️⃣ Verify Static Files in FastAPI</h1>
<p data-start="317" data-end="364">Open <strong data-start="322" data-end="335"><code data-start="324" data-end="333">main.py</code></strong> and make sure you have this:</p>
