<hr data-start="348" data-end="351">
<h1 data-start="353" data-end="403">1️⃣ Add Floating Animation (Cards Move Slightly)</h1>
<p data-start="405" data-end="447">Add this to the <strong data-start="421" data-end="446">bottom of <code data-start="433" data-end="444">style.css</code></strong>:</p>
