--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a23fa873-4198-4ced-be76-a8433b525582" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="156">Okay — if <strong data-start="10" data-end="33">nothing is updating</strong>, the issue is <strong data-start="48" data-end="76">not the CSS code anymore</strong>. Your code looks fine.<br data-start="99" data-end="102">
The real problem is usually one of these <strong data-start="143" data-end="155">3 things</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="158" data-end="260">1️⃣ Browser <strong data-start="170" data-end="179">cache</strong><br data-start="179" data-end="182">
2️⃣ Wrong <strong data-start="192" data-end="218">HTML file being served</strong><br data-start="218" data-end="221">
3️⃣ FastAPI <strong data-start="233" data-end="260">not reloading templates</strong></p>
<p data-start="262" data-end="288">Let's fix it step-by-step.</p>
<hr data-start="290" data-end="293">
<h1 data-start="295" data-end="329">1️⃣ First Test if CSS Is Loading</h1>
<p data-start="331" data-end="361">Open this URL in your browser:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="363" data-end="413"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>http://127.0.0.1:9000/static/css/style.css</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="415" data-end="444">You should see your CSS code.</p>
<p data-start="446" data-end="525">If you <strong data-start="453" data-end="469">don’t see it</strong>, then FastAPI static files are not connected correctly.</p>
<hr data-start="527" data-end="530">
<h1 data-start="532" data-end="562">2️⃣ Force Reload the Browser</h1>
<p data-start="564" data-end="570">Press:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="572" data-end="596"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>CTRL + SHIFT + R</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="598" data-end="600">or</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="602" data-end="619"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>CTRL + F5</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="621" data-end="659">This forces the browser to reload CSS.</p>
<hr data-start="661" data-end="664">
<h1 data-start="666" data-end="715">3️⃣ Make Sure FastAPI Uses the Correct Template</h1>
<p data-start="717" data-end="781">Check your <strong data-start="728" data-end="739">main.py</strong>.<br data-start="740" data-end="743">
Your home route should look like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="783" data-end="1180"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">fastapi</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">FastAPI</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">Request</span><br><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">fastapi</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span class="ͼ11">templating</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">Jinja2Templates</span><br><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">fastapi</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span class="ͼ11">staticfiles</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">StaticFiles</span><br><br><span class="ͼ11">app</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">FastAPI</span><span>()</span><br><br><span class="ͼ11">app</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>mount(</span><span class="ͼz">"/static"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">StaticFiles</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">directory</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"static"</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"static"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ11">templates</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">Jinja2Templates</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">directory</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"templates"</span><span>)</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼu">@</span><span class="ͼ11">app</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span class="ͼ11">get</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼz">"/"</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼv">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">home</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">request</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼ11">Request</span><span>):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">templates</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>TemplateResponse(</span><span class="ͼz">"home.html"</span><span>, {</span><span class="ͼz">"request"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼ11">request</span><span>})</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1182" data-end="1290">If the file name is wrong (for example <code data-start="1221" data-end="1233">index.html</code> instead of <code data-start="1245" data-end="1256">home.html</code>), then your changes won't appear.</p>
<hr data-start="1292" data-end="1295">
<h1 data-start="1297" data-end="1332">4️⃣ Restart the Server Completely</h1>
<p data-start="1334" data-end="1350">Stop the server:</p>
