argin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="95b678e6-eb57-4359-bd1f-f1c9fd470e42" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="214">Thanks for sharing the code. Your CSS and HTML are mostly fine now. If <strong data-start="71" data-end="98">you still see no change</strong>, the issue is almost certainly <strong data-start="130" data-end="191">browser cache or the server still serving an old template</strong>. Let’s verify quickly.</p>
<hr data-start="216" data-end="219">
<h2 data-start="221" data-end="267">1️⃣ Confirm the server is using <code data-start="256" data-end="267">home.html</code></h2>
<p data-start="269" data-end="316">Open <strong data-start="274" data-end="287"><code data-start="276" data-end="285">main.py</code></strong> and check the route for <code data-start="312" data-end="315">/</code>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="318" data-end="713"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Python</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost border-token-border-default ms-2 border font-sans" aria-label="Run code" type="button"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-ms-0.5 icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#6ef7a4" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Run</div></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">fastapi</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">FastAPI</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">Request</span><br><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">fastapi</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span class="ͼ11">templating</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">Jinja2Templates</span><br><span class="ͼv">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">fastapi</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span class="ͼ11">staticfiles</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">StaticFiles</span><br><br><span class="ͼ11">app</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">FastAPI</span><span>()</span><br><br><span class="ͼ11">app</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>mount(</span><span class="ͼz">"/static"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ11">StaticFiles</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">directory</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"static"</span><span>), </span><span class="ͼ11">name</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"static"</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼ11">templates</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">Jinja2Templates</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">directory</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"templates"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼu">@</span><span class="ͼ11">app</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span class="ͼ11">get</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼz">"/"</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼv">def</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">home</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼ11">request</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼ11">Request</span><span>):</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">return</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ11">templates</span><span class="ͼv">.</span><span>TemplateResponse(</span><span class="ͼz">"home.html"</span><span>, {</span><span class="ͼz">"request"</span><span>: </span><span class="ͼ11">request</span><span>})</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="715" data-end="789">If it says <code data-start="726" data-end="740">"index.html"</code> instead of <code data-start="752" data-end="765">"home.html"</code>, your edits won’t show.</p>
<hr data-start="791" data-end="794">
<h2 data-start="796" data-end="827">2️⃣ Hard refresh the browser</h2>
<p data-start="829" data-end="849">Do <strong data-start="832" data-end="848">one of these</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="851" data-end="875"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>CTRL + SHIFT + R</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="877" data-end="879">or</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="881" data-end="898"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>CTRL + F5</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="900" data-end="947">This forces the browser to reload CSS and HTML.</p>
<hr data-start="949" data-end="952">
<h2 data-start="954" data-end="987">3️⃣ Restart the FastAPI server</h2>
<p data-start="989" data-end="1005">Stop the server:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1007" data-end="1023"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>CTRL + C</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
