<p data-start="1104" data-end="1124">Example explanation:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1126" data-end="1281">
<p data-start="1128" data-end="1281">The backend of the Smart AI Food Advisor system is developed using <strong data-start="1195" data-end="1206">FastAPI</strong>, a modern Python web framework used to build APIs quickly and efficiently.</p>
