<p data-start="942" data-end="959">Important things:</p>
<ul data-start="961" data-end="1049">
<li data-start="961" data-end="1002">
<p data-start="963" data-end="1002"><code data-start="963" data-end="983">@app.get("/login")</code> → shows login page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1003" data-end="1049">
<p data-start="1005" data-end="1049"><code data-start="1005" data-end="1026">@app.post("/login")</code> → processes login form</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1051" data-end="1067">Both must exist.</p>
<hr data-start="1069" data-end="1072">
