<p data-start="245" data-end="319">means <strong data-start="251" data-end="318">FastAPI did not receive <code data-start="277" data-end="287">username</code> and <code data-start="292" data-end="302">password</code> from the form</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="321" data-end="369">So the issue is in <strong data-start="340" data-end="368"><code data-start="342" data-end="354">login.html</code> form inputs</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="371" data-end="374">
<h1 data-start="376" data-end="398">✅ Correct Login Form</h1>
<p data-start="400" data-end="442">Your form must look <strong data-start="420" data-end="441">exactly like this</strong>:</p>
