<p data-start="127" data-end="168">Right now your system already calculates:</p>
<ul data-start="170" data-end="212">
<li data-start="170" data-end="175">
<p data-start="172" data-end="175">BMI</p>
</li>
<li data-start="176" data-end="191">
<p data-start="178" data-end="191">Health status</p>
</li>
<li data-start="192" data-end="203">
<p data-start="194" data-end="203">Nutrition</p>
</li>
<li data-start="204" data-end="212">
<p data-start="206" data-end="212">Advice</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="214" data-end="265">We will now add <strong data-start="230" data-end="264">recommended foods for the user</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="267" data-end="270">
