<p data-start="760" data-end="812">This will make the background <strong data-start="790" data-end="811">darker and softer</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="814" data-end="817">
<h1 data-start="819" data-end="860">2️⃣ Improve the Form Card (Glass Style)</h1>
