="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/apple.png"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"floating apple"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/banana.png"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"floating banana"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/carrot.png"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"floating carrot"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/broccoli.png"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"floating broccoli"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/avocado.png"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"floating avocado"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1105" data-end="1123">Example structure:</p>
