<hr data-start="1424" data-end="1427">
<h1 data-start="1429" data-end="1456">Step 3 — Add Floating CSS</h1>
<p data-start="1458" data-end="1501">Add this <strong data-start="1467" data-end="1500">inside your <code data-start="1481" data-end="1490">&lt;style&gt;</code> section</strong>.</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1503" data-end="1965"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">/* floating food images */</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼ10">floating</span><span>{</span><br><span>position:</span><span class="ͼy">absolute</span><span>;</span><br><span>width:</span><span class="ͼy">80</span><span class="ͼv">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>animation:</span><span class="ͼy">float</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">6</span><span class="ͼv">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">ease-in-out</span><span> </span><span class="ͼy">infinite</span><span>;</span><br><span>opacity:</span><span class="ͼy">0.9</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">/* positions */</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼ10">apple</span><span>{</span><br><span>top:</span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>left:</span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼ10">banana</span><span>{</span><br><span>top:</span><span class="ͼy">20</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>right:</span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼ10">carrot</span><span>{</span><br><span>bottom:</span><span class="ͼy">15</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>left:</span><span class="ͼy">15</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼ10">broccoli</span><span>{</span><br><span>bottom:</span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>right:</span><span class="ͼy">10</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼ10">avocado</span><span>{</span><br><span>top:</span><span class="ͼy">50</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>left:</span><span class="ͼy">5</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼt">/* floating animation */</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">@keyframes</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ13">float</span><span>{</span><br><span class="ͼy">0</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>{transform:</span><span class="ͼv">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span class="ͼv">px</span><span>);}</span><br><span class="ͼy">50</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>{transform:</span><span class="ͼv">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼy">-20</span><span class="ͼv">px</span><span>);}</span><br><span class="ͼy">100</span><span class="ͼv">%</span><span>{transform:</span><span class="ͼv">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span class="ͼv">px</span><span>);}</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1967" data-end="1970">
<h1 data-start="1972" data-end="2004">Step 4 — Use Simple Background</h1>
<p data-start="2006" data-end="2033">Use a <strong data-start="2012" data-end="2032">clean background</strong>:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2035" data-end="2105"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ13">body</span><span>{</span><br><span>background:</span><span class="ͼv">linear-gradient</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼy">135</span><span class="ͼv">deg</span><span>,#0f172a,#1e293b);</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2107" data-end="2110">
<h1 data-start="2112" data-end="2120">Result</h1>
<p data-start="2122" data-end="2177">Your page will look like a <strong data-start="2149" data-end="2176">modern nutrition app UI</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="2179" data-end="2262">
<li data-start="2179" data-end="2204">
<p data-start="2181" data-end="2204">Clean dark background</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2205" data-end="2239">
<p data-start="2207" data-end="2239">Floating fruits and vegetables</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2240" data-end="2262">
<p data-start="2242" data-end="2262">Centered form card</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2264" data-end="2298">Much better than the busy pattern.</p>
<hr data-start="2300" data-end="2303">
