 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="181">Adding <strong data-start="7" data-end="42">10,000 separate images manually</strong> is not practical and will also <strong data-start="74" data-end="108">slow down your website heavily</strong>. A page with 10,000 <code data-start="129" data-end="136">&lt;img&gt;</code> elements will make the browser very slow. 🚫</p>
<p data-start="183" data-end="396">Instead, the correct professional method is to use <strong data-start="234" data-end="282">one image pattern repeated in the background</strong>. This gives the effect of <strong data-start="309" data-end="368">thousands of small food images randomly across the page</strong> but keeps the website fast.</p>
<p data-start="398" data-end="454">I'll show you the <strong data-start="416" data-end="454">best way to achieve what you want.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h1 data-start="461" data-end="503">1️⃣ Use the Image as a Repeating Pattern</h1>
<p data-start="505" data-end="537">Save the image you generated as:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="539" data-end="575"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>static/images/food-icons.png</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="577" data-end="580">
