rong data-start="19" data-end="41">boxes/grid pattern</strong> is because the image is <strong data-start="66" data-end="88">repeating as tiles</strong>. That creates the square pattern.</p>
<p data-start="124" data-end="214">What you want is <strong data-start="141" data-end="191">random food icons spread across the background</strong>, not repeating blocks.</p>
<p data-start="216" data-end="315">There are <strong data-start="226" data-end="238">two ways</strong>, but the best one is using <strong data-start="266" data-end="314">CSS with a larger background and random look</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="317" data-end="320">
<h1 data-start="322" data-end="371">Method 1 — Use One Large Background (No Repeat)</h1>
<p data-start="373" data-end="405">Replace your body CSS with this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="407" data-end="698"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ13">body</span><span>{</span><br><span>font-family:</span><span class="ͼz">'Poppins'</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼy">sans-serif</span><span>;</span><br><span>background-image:</span><span class="ͼy">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/foods.png"</span><span>);</span><br><span>background-size:</span><span class="ͼy">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>background-position:</span><span class="ͼy">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>background-repeat:</span><span class="ͼy">no-repeat</span><span>;</span><br><span>background-color:#0f172a;</span><br><br><span>margin:</span><span class="ͼy">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>height:</span><span class="ͼy">100</span><span class="ͼv">vh</span><span>;</span><br><span>display:</span><span class="ͼy">flex</span><span>;</span><br><span>justify-content:</span><span class="ͼy">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>align-items:</span><span class="ͼy">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="700" data-end="732">This removes the <strong data-start="717" data-end="731">box tiling</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="734" data-end="737">
<h1 data-start="739" data-end="783">Method 2 — Make Icons Smaller But Not Grid</h1>
<p data-start="785" data-end="789">Use:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="791" data-end="850"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div 