<p data-start="981" data-end="1032">This makes the pattern <strong data-start="1004" data-end="1031">less visible as squares</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1034" data-end="1037">
<h1 data-start="1039" data-end="1083">Method 3 (Best UI) — Floating Random Foods</h1>
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1162">Professional websites usually use <strong data-start="1119" data-end="1161">floating icons instead of tiled images</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1164" data-end="1179">Example effect:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1181" data-end="1271"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fk4oovux.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>🍎       🥑        🍌</span><br><br><span>      User Health Form</span><br><br><span>🥦      🍓       🥕</span><br><br><span>   🍅       🍍</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1273" data-end="1313">Icons appear <strong data-start="1286" data-end="1312">random instead of grid</strong>.</p>
