<p data-start="99" data-end="151">I’ll show you <strong data-start="113" data-end="150">exactly how to do it step-by-step</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="153" data-end="156">
<h1 data-start="158" data-end="186">1️⃣ Keep a Dark Background</h1>
<p data-start="188" data-end="224">In your CSS change the <code data-start="211" data-end="217">body</code> style:</p>
