<p data-start="95" data-end="189">You need to place the images <strong data-start="124" data-end="188">inside the <code data-start="137" data-end="145">&lt;body&gt;</code> but BEFORE the form card (<code data-start="172" data-end="185">health-card</code>)</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="191" data-end="194">
<h1 data-start="196" data-end="249">Step 2 — Add Floating Food Images in <code data-start="235" data-end="249">details.html</code></h1>
<p data-start="251" data-end="278">Open your <strong data-start="261" data-end="277">details.html</strong>.</p>
