an class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"food food7"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">src</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"/static/images/orange.png"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"food food8"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼ13">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ12">class</span><span class="ͼv">=</span><span class="ͼz">"health-card"</span><span class="ͼ13">&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="894" data-end="920">So your structure becomes:</p>
