<p data-start="47" data-end="171">Those <strong data-start="53" data-end="69">broken icons</strong> mean the browser <strong data-start="87" data-end="118">cannot find the image files</strong>. That is why you see the small broken image symbols.</p>
<p data-start="173" data-end="240">So Step 2 is correct, but the <strong data-start="203" data-end="239">image paths or files are missing</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="242" data-end="255">Let's fix it.</p>
<hr data-start="257" data-end="260">
<h1 data-start="262" data-end="304">1️⃣ Put the Images in the Correct Folder</h1>
<p data-start="306" data-end="346">Inside your project, make sure you have:</p>
